🔒 Security Features
Role-based access control (each user only sees what they need)
Account status system (Pending / Approved / Disapproved)
Activity logging with timestamps for accountability
Input validation on all forms
---
📌 Limitations
Data is stored in a local JSON file (not a full database)
No password hashing (passwords stored as plain text)
Single-user access (no simultaneous multi-user support)
No internet/web access — desktop only
---
